Do you KNOW many Endgame wizards?  Sorry that sounds as bad as it does, but I can't figure a better way to ask it.  With VASTLY increased many pools, and significantly increased Foci effects (including their own Rizlona pet if a bard isnt handy a wizard's overall DPS is generally accepted to be 50 to 100% higher going from relatively stock 61 to Time geared, from the stuff I have read and from wizards I know who are parse junkies.  (I have heard people quote higher, but have not seen any real substantiation)
<br />

<br />
Clickie pants are VERY important to endgame wizards, because they allow them to reach their potential.  You cannot reasonably exclude them from the issue, because even though they reduce the THEORETICAL maximum DPS, they increase the real maximum.  Clickie pants are LESS important on XP grind mobs since they tend to die too fast.
<br />

<br />
